1
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:40,360
May I be like the stars

2
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,580
and you like the moon.

3
00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:43,670
As long as the world remains,

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,780
so shall we.

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

6
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,370
I want to be with you forever.

8
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

9
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,480
You and she are ultimately different.

10
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,600
Have you ever

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,789
truly cared for me?

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,250
No.

13
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,360
Never.

14
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:57,720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

15
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,310
May we live and die together,

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,040
and share life and death as one.

17
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:45,790
[Moonlight Mystique]

18
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:49,980
[Episode 28]

19
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,550
Master?

20
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:08,720
What exactly happened at Cold Spring Palace?

21
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:11,290
Why did Fan Yue suddenly attack it?

22
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,410
I don't know, Master.

23
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,160
At the time, the situation was dire,

24
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:15,850
so I had no choice but to leave first.

25
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,550
Leaving was for the best.

26
00:03:18,090 --> 00:03:19,820
Zhen Yu was defeated by Fan Yue

27
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,780
and fled with severe injuries.

28
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:23,840
This is already widely known.

29
00:03:23,860 --> 00:03:25,030
After this battle,

30
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:28,870
Cold Spring Palace will surely remain in hiding for a while.

31
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:31,490
You've had a hard time these days.

32
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,090
Come back to Lanling with me.

33
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,680
Your uncles have been missing you.

34
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:40,160
What are you doing?

35
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:41,660
Master, please save Fu Ling.

36
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,210
Fu Ling?

37
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:44,820
Zhen Yu's disciple?

38
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:46,410
She's here now?

39
00:03:46,610 --> 00:03:47,490
Yes.

40
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:51,890
You're out of your mind!

41
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:54,470
How could you involve yourself with a demon?

42
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:56,220
Fu Ling has saved me many times,

43
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,870
even at the risk of punishment from Zhen Yu.

44
00:03:58,070 --> 00:03:59,430
Now, she has left Cold Spring

45
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:00,560
and has no further ties with Zhen Yu.

46
00:04:00,870 --> 00:04:01,990
Please, Master, save her.

47
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:03,810
Even if she has left Cold Spring,

48
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:05,230
she is still a demon!

49
00:04:05,250 --> 00:04:06,840
How can you forget all the wrongs she's done

50
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,670
just because you're feeling merciful now?

51
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:10,070
She's not a demon!

52
00:04:11,410 --> 00:04:12,450
What are you saying?

53
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,960
She's Bai Xi,

54
00:04:14,850 --> 00:04:16,290
Bai Xun's daughter,

55
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,019
and Shuo's older sister.

56
00:04:19,529 --> 00:04:20,920
What's going on?

57
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:22,140
10 years ago,

58
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:23,900
Zhen Yu took Bai Xi from the Bai family,

59
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:25,820
erased her memories,

60
00:04:25,850 --> 00:04:27,190
and infused her with demonic power,

61
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,700
turning her into a demon.

62
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:31,540
I've only recently found out that she's Bai Xi.

63
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:33,920
Why did Zhen Yu do this?

64
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:35,280
I don't know.

65
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,770
But Xi is innocent.

66
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,880
She was deceived by Zhen Yu,

67
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:40,530
which led her to commit many wrongdoings.

68
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:42,900
She suffers from guilt now.

69
00:04:42,930 --> 00:04:44,080
Master,

70
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,600
Xi was originally human.

71
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:46,950
Please save her.

72
00:04:47,909 --> 00:04:49,100
Chong Zhao,

73
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,200
Fu Ling has done too much evil.

74
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:54,220
Even if she was once a human,

75
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,090
after becoming a demon,

76
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,770
everything she has done is her own doing.

77
00:04:59,610 --> 00:05:02,230
Moreover, she now carries demonic power.

78
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:03,450
She has already become a demon.

79
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,190
I cannot save her.

80
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:05,930
Master...

81
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,680
