100
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,740
I want to stay here

101
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,100
to be with her

102
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,710
and protect her.

103
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,810
Everything you've suffered

104
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,940
has been for Lanling.

105
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,740
