114
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:40,370
Fu Ling is no longer the Bai Xi she once was.

115
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,750
Don't get too entangled with her.

116
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:43,659
Otherwise...

117
00:06:46,730 --> 00:06:48,960
