122
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:38,900
But rest assured.

123
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:42,040
I'll definitely capture Fan Yue

124
00:07:42,409 --> 00:07:43,920
and Bai Shuo

125
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:45,990
