227
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:22,030
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

228
00:11:19,170 --> 00:11:21,240
Take care of yourself.

229
00:11:23,050 --> 00:11:26,410
♫That year, that year♫

230
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:30,250
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

231
