00:39:09,370 --> 00:39:10,450
No.

834
00:39:10,470 --> 00:39:11,990
You can't trust anyone in Lanling.

835
00:39:12,020 --> 00:39:14,270
Your master could also be the one who killed your mother.

836
00:39:14,290 --> 00:39:15,250
Impossible.

837
00:39:15,970 --> 00:39:18,020
My master and my parents had a deep bond.

838
00:39:18,040 --> 00:39:19,000
If it were my master,

839
00:39:19,030 --> 00:39:20,610
he wouldn't have raised me himself.

840
00:39:21,010 --> 00:39:23,120
Anyone in this world might hurt me,

841
00:39:23,140 --> 00:39:24,490
but my master would never.

842
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:25,440
Moreover,

843
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:27,270
my master has been protecting people his whole life.

844
00:39:27,300 --> 00:39:29,090
He would never do such a thing.

845
00:39:34,490 --> 00:39:37,420
[Bodhi Village]

846
00:39:41,650 --> 00:39:43,690
The compass led us here.

847
00:39:43,720 --> 00:39:44,950
Is my master

848
00:39:44,970 --> 00:39:46,510
in this village?

849
00:39:46,610 --> 00:39:48,380
Do you know this village?

850
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:51,290
I've never heard of such a place on the Eastern Continent.

851
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:55,200
But the compass is clearly pointing towards the village.

852
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:56,570
Why don't we go in and have a look?

853
00:39:56,870 --> 00:39:58,230
A single village,

854
00:39:58,400 --> 00:39:59,770
hidden in the mountains.

855
00:39:59,790 --> 00:40:00,500
It's rather strange.

856
00:40:01,180 --> 00:40:02,380
Stay close to me after going in.

857
00:40:03,170 --> 00:40:04,290
Let's go.

858
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,510
Here, take it if you like.

859
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:09,600
-Old wine.
-Pumpkins.

860
00:40:09,630 --> 00:40:10,720
Fresh pumpkins.

861
00:40:10,740 --> 00:40:12,050
Take one with you.

862
00:40:12,430 --> 00:40:13,950
-Take a look.
-Take one. Take one.

863
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:15,290
So fresh.

864
00:40:19,620 --> 00:40:20,910
Thank you, sir.

865
00:40:21,510 --> 00:40:22,150
It smells so good.

866
00:40:23,450 --> 00:40:25,140
Why are there humans

867
00:40:25,170 --> 00:40:26,480
on the land of the Eternals?

868
00:40:26,500 --> 00:40:27,750
They all have mana.

869
00:40:28,180 --> 00:40:28,970
They're not humans.

870
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:33,200
This village is not simple.

871
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:34,320
Be cautious.

872
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,110
Come look.

873
00:40:37,110 --> 00:40:38,340
Miss, take a look.

874
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:45,110
Have a look. Fresh fruit.

875
00:40:45,130 --> 00:40:46,820
Miss, come back again.

876
00:40:46,850 --> 00:40:47,520
Thank you, madam.

877
00:40:47,540 --> 00:40:49,060
Sir, the wontons are really good.

878
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,510
I'll pack some for you.

879
00:40:50,770 --> 00:40:51,520
Take care.

880
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:52,790
Sir.

881
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:54,630
We were out for a walk

882
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:55,700
and stumbled upon this place.

883
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,110
May I ask where this is?

884
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:58,230
This is Bodhi Village.

885
00:40:58,230 --> 00:40:59,650
You're here because you're meant to be.

886
00:40:59,670 --> 00:41:01,020
Welcome.

887
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:01,990
Meant to be?

888
00:41:02,010 --> 00:41:02,660
Yes.

889
00:41:02,690 --> 00:41:04,440
This village is protected by the Divine Maiden.

890
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:05,510
Whether you're on the run,

891
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:06,550
homeless,

892
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:07,810
or seeking to avoid the mundane world,

893
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:08,760
if fate brings you here,

894
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:09,960
the Divine Maiden will take you in,

895
00:41:09,990 --> 00:41:10,800
never asking about your past

896
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,640
and treating everyone equally.

897
00:41:11,670 --> 00:41:12,500
The Divine Maiden?

898
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:13,850
That's right. This village

899
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:15,320
owes everything to the Divine Maiden.

900
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:17,020
[Food]

901
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,920
We were all saved by her.

902
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:17,710
Yes.

903
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:19,670
The Divine Maiden is not only powerful

904
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:21,510
but also very compassionate.

905
00:41:21,690 --> 00:41:22,770
She's the kindest person

906
00:41:22,790 --> 00:41:24,620
in the world.

907
00:41:24,650 --> 00:41:26,010
If you meet her,

908
00:41:26,030 --> 00:41:27,510
you'll definitely like her too.

909
00:41:27,550 --> 00:41:28,280
Definitely, you'll like her.

910
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:28,840
Yes.

911
00:41:28,860 --> 00:41:29,970
Yes, you will.

912
00:41:30,890 --> 00:41:32,530
Let's go over there.

913
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,920
Do you think the Divine Maiden

914
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:38,830
they spoke of is real?

915
00:41:38,850 --> 00:41:40,040
Whether real or not,

916
00:41:40,380 --> 00:41:41,980
someone who can hide so much spiritual energy

917
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,080
and keep it a secret

918
00:41:43,640 --> 00:41:44,910
is definitely not an ordinary person.

919
00:41:47,820 --> 00:41:48,410
Look.

920
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:49,400
The Divine Maiden is here!

921
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:52,980
I told you,

922
00:41:53,010 --> 00:41:54,300
once you come to this village,

923
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:55,880
we're all family.

924
00:41:55,900 --> 00:41:57,110
No need for formalities.

925
00:41:57,140 --> 00:41:59,170
Just do your own thing.

926
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,460
Divine Maiden,

927
00:42:27,490 --> 00:42:28,220
you...

928
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,590
I've finally found you.

929
00:42:47,170 --> 00:42:47,850
What...

930
00:42:47,870 --> 00:42:49,140
What's going on?

931
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:50,750
I don't know.

932
00:42:50,770 --> 00:42:52,400
What's wrong with the Divine Maiden?

933
00:42:53,630 --> 00:42:54,500
Is he the one

934
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:56,080
the Divine Maiden has been waiting for?

935
00:42:56,110 --> 00:42:57,400
No way.

936
00:42:57,420 --> 00:42:59,140
The Divine Maiden has been waiting for him all this time,

937
00:42:59,430 --> 00:43:00,320
but now he has

938
00:43:00,340 --> 00:43:02,170
another woman by his side.

939
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:06,840
The Divine Maiden must be heartbroken.

940
00:43:07,730 --> 00:43:09,550
What does she mean?

941
00:43:11,050 --> 00:43:12,080
Do you two know each other?

942
00:43:18,820 --> 00:43:19,760
I've never met her.

943
00:43:20,650 --> 00:43:21,920
You don't remember me?

944
00:43:27,540 --> 00:43:29,530
Yeah, 60,000 years is so long

945
00:43:29,870 --> 00:43:30,750
that

946
00:43:30,780 --> 00:43:32,010
you've forgotten everything.

947
00:43:34,520 --> 00:43:35,770
It's okay.

948
00:43:34,570 --> 00:43:37,350
[Food]

949
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:36,640
If you've forgotten me,

950
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:38,090
we'll just get to know each other again.

951
00:43:38,790 --> 00:43:40,390
In scattered flowers and flying petals,

952
00:43:40,560 --> 00:43:42,250
my once youthful face has changed.

953
00:43:42,460 --> 00:43:44,110
Now, I go by the name

954
00:43:44,000 --> 00:43:45,330
[Luan Zhu, Divine Race]

955
00:43:44,140 --> 00:43:45,140
Luan Zhu.

956
00:43:53,630 --> 00:43:55,100
Ms. Luan Zhu,

957
00:43:55,120 --> 00:43:56,760
why not let me get to know you as well?

958
00:43:58,190 --> 00:43:59,440
You're a human?

959
00:43:59,690 --> 00:44:00,690
Yes.

960
00:44:00,710 --> 00:44:01,860
Bai Shuo, a human.

961
00:44:02,760 --> 00:44:03,760
It's getting late.

962
00:44:03,800 --> 00:44:05,370
I'll skip the pleasantries.

963
00:44:05,400 --> 00:44:06,590
We came to this village

964
00:44:06,670 --> 00:44:08,000
to look for someone.

965
00:44:08,360 --> 00:44:10,520
Have there been any other visitors besides us

966
00:44:10,540 --> 00:44:12,150
in the past several days?

967
00:44:13,750 --> 00:44:14,500
Well...

968
00:44:16,570 --> 00:44:17,870
Shuo!
